{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/articles/2018/02/02/1546344578809.html","result":{"data":{"asciidoc":{"id":"e71e2ffc-dbf4-58ec-bbb6-10f24a0af49b","fields":{"slug":"/articles/2018/02/02/1546344578809.html","birthTime":"2018-02-02T00:08:00.000Z","modifiedTime":"2019-01-01T12:48:10.931Z"},"html":"<div class=\"olist arabic\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>通过 SecureCRT 连接到阿里云 CentOS7 服务器；</p>\n</li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>进入到目录 /usr/local/ 中：</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">cd /usr/local/</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"olist arabic\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\" start=\"3\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>创建目录 tools：</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\"> mkdir -p tools</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"olist arabic\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\" start=\"4\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>进入到目录 /usr/local/tools 中：</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\"> cd tools/</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"olist arabic\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\" start=\"5\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>下载 jdk-8u91-linux-x64.tar.gz：</p>\n<div class=\"ulist\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<ul data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>wget –no-check-certificate –no-cookies –header ``Cookie:\noraclelicense=accept-securebackup-cookie''\n<a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/otn-pub/java/jdk/7u71-b14/jdk-7u71-linux-x64.rpm\" class=\"bare\">http://download.oracle.com/otn-pub/java/jdk/7u71-b14/jdk-7u71-linux-x64.rpm</a></p>\n</li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html\">官网地址</a>，找到需要的，然后加上头既可</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>加压缩 jdk-8u91-linux-x64.tar.gz 文件：</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\"> tar -zxvf jdk-8u91-linux-x64.tar.gz</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"olist arabic\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\" start=\"7\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>返回到上一级并创建 /usr/local/jdk 目录： <code>`</code></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">cd .. mkdir -p jdk</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"olist arabic\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\" start=\"8\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>进入到 tools 目录后将 jdk1.8.0_91 移动到 jdk 目录中：</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">cd ../tools/ mv jdk1.8.0_91/ ../jdk/</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"olist arabic\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\" start=\"9\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>打开 /etc/ 目录下的 profile 文件：</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">vi /etc/profile</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"olist arabic\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\" start=\"10\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>将如下代码追加到 profile 文件末尾：</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\"># idea - jdk8 settings start 2016-05-01\n\nJAVA_HOME=/usr/local/jdk/jdk1.8.0_91\nJRE_HOME=$JAVA_HOME/jre\nPATH=$PATH:$JAVA_HOME/bin:$JRE_HOME/bin\nCLASSPATH=:$JAVA_HOME/lib/dt.jar:$JAVA_HOME/lib/tools.jar:$JRE_HOME/lib/dt.jar\nexport JAVA_HOME JRE_HOME PATH CLASSPATH\n\n# idea - jdk8 settings end - 2016-05-01</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"olist arabic\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\" start=\"11\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>按 Esc 键、输入 wq! 回车，保持并退出。即可启用新的配置：<code>source /etc/profile</code></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"olist arabic\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\" start=\"12\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>输入 java -version 查看 JDK 的版本：</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\"> [root@iZ94hws2fzlZ jdk1.8.0_91]# java -version\n java version \"1.8.0_91\"\n Java(TM) SE Runtime Environment (build 1.8.0_91-b14)\n Java HotSpot(TM) 64-Bit Server VM (build 25.91-b14, mixed mode)</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>","document":{"title":"[归档] CentOS7 上安装 JDK1.8"},"pageAttributes":{"category":"归档","description":"CentOS7 上安装 JDK1.8","image":"https://img.hacpai.com/bing/20190221.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1280/h/720/interlace/1/q/100","sort":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/articles/2018/02/02/1546344578809.html","next":{"document":{"title":"[归档] CentOS7 64位下 MySQL5.7 安装与配置（YUM）"},"fields":{"slug":"/articles/2018/02/02/1546344583722.html"}},"previous":{"document":{"title":"[归档] 《java语言与面向对象程序设计》清华大学出版社 课后习题 答案"},"fields":{"slug":"/articles/2018/01/01/1546344577314.html"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3069561552","3673333084"]}